= Design =

== Usability by Default ==

While developed with security-focused design goals, {{project_name_long}} remains highly flexible. The layered approach to security allows applications to retain usability. {{project_name_long}} can be used for everyday "general-purpose computing" or for more risky activities that require a highly advanced security-centric platform. Since {{project_name_long}} is [[Reasons for Freedom Software|Freedom Software]] users may install any application of their choosing -- no restrictions are placed on how {{project_name_long}} can be used, customized or modified.

